 strong enough to ensure that the desired trickle down effect works.
 
\end_layout

\end_inset

.
 When the distribution of assets such as education are assisted by the state,
 the expected risk in levels in education themselves is clearly lowered.
 Thus, how much education eventually matters towards status may depend on
